General.Name: AcouSort AB
General.Description: AcouSort AB (publ), a technology company, develops products and solutions for automated preparation of biological samples based on acoustofluidics technology for researchers and life science companies. It offers AcouTrap, a benchtop research instrument for sample preparation of cells, extracellular vesicles, bacteria, and viruses from various media; AcouPlasma, an integrated blood plasma separation module that enables in-line analysis of blood plasma from whole blood samples; and AcouWash, a benchtop research instrument for label-free separation of target cells from various samples. AcouSort AB (publ) has collaboration agreement with global life science company to develop cell therapy. The company was founded in 2010 and is based in Lund, Sweden.
